295
00:27:24,881 --> 00:27:28,047
Pass the message as you go.
Tell everybody.

296
00:27:34,297 --> 00:27:36,381
Seven minutes!

297
00:27:36,464 --> 00:27:39,422
The power failure lasted seven minutes!

298
00:27:39,464 --> 00:27:41,381
Twice as long as we've ever had!

299
00:27:41,422 --> 00:27:43,381
* It was so strong *

