00:28:59,714 --> 00:29:02,464
You're ruining the couch, Granny.

314
00:29:04,756 --> 00:29:08,297
You-You found it.

315
00:29:09,881 --> 00:29:12,339
- This is what you're looking for?
- Uh-huh.

316
00:29:12,422 --> 00:29:14,339
Are you sure?

317
00:29:16,714 --> 00:29:18,255
What's so special about it?

318
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:24,630
I don't- I forget. I don't remember.

319
00:29:28,297 --> 00:29:31,130
I don't remember.

320
00:29:32,755 --> 00:29:34,672
Okay, Granny.
I've gotta get back to work.

