00:29:54,922 --> 00:29:57,089
The Generator's broken.
It's hopeless.

326
00:29:57,172 --> 00:29:59,380
<i>Next load!</i>

327
00:29:59,464 --> 00:30:02,589
<i>I have a message for Seely Schnap.</i>

328
00:30:02,672 --> 00:30:05,172
<i>I'm Seely Schnap. What is it?</i>

329
00:30:05,255 --> 00:30:07,714
- Munn Millders sent me.
