00:33:58,963 --> 00:34:00,963
What can you do about it?

382
00:34:01,047 --> 00:34:02,963
Hmm?

383
00:34:04,297 --> 00:34:07,213
<i>What can you do about it?</i>

384
00:34:18,547 --> 00:34:21,588
How do you explain
that this used to be so small?

385
00:34:26,088 --> 00:34:28,505
You're gonna
give yourself a headache.

386
00:34:58,463 --> 00:35:00,338
"Ember. "

387
00:35:02,213 --> 00:35:03,922
"Time. "

388
00:35:06,713 --> 00:35:09,380
"Support life. "

389
00:35:15,088 --> 00:35:17,088
"One: Proceed. "

