00:36:04,963 --> 00:36:07,213
- Next!
- I need help right now, please!

401
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:18,838
- Did-Did we find it?
- Lie back, Roo.

402
00:36:18,921 --> 00:36:20,963
- Did we-
